           <a href="https://www.credly.com/earner/earned/badge/44e397f5-6eb7-42a1-b44e-de891886e29b" target="_blank" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-2xl border border-zinc-200 dark:border-white/5 hover:bg-zinc-100 dark:hover:bg-white/5 transition-all">
